{"tid":1439144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"痴撚線，打開電視，有線，Now tv全撚部唔講人話","createTime":"2019-08-10T04:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T12:32:15.000Z","uid":38177,"like":37,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7937803663caf0746ac1813835060fe3811fae3e","tid":1439144,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:15:48.000Z","msg":"撐警既撐警<br />\n譴責暴力既譴責暴力<br />\n仲要繼續支持政府<br />\n而家警察<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無法無天，濫權濫捕</span>到一個地步<br />\n<br />\n仲可以有依啲泯滅人性既言論出現<br />\n<br />\n除咗武力升級，真係無其他路行<br />\n<br />\n見到社會越來越荒謬，媒體越來越不堪<br />\n<br />\n真係核彈都唔割席，依啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">顛倒是非黑白</span></span>既地方，就係香港人想要既香港？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非同勇武缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"737f78ddcb8e3e1e5a5f830fd7b10db74cf3ff6f","tid":1439144,"uid":274136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:20:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人重點日程：<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月9-11日</strong>：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月10日</strong>：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月11日</strong>：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n<strong>8月11日</strong>：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">逢星期五，日擺買！減少家庭支出</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9c188ca27e87b173ddd01ab64861bd600c36269d","tid":1439144,"uid":38177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:36:23.000Z","msg":"試問邊一個香港人，睇到警察濫捕，暴力拘捕，企圖謀殺香港人，仲可以支持警察？<br />\n<br />\n試問邊一個香港人，落到街，見到示威者既和平，分派物資既自律，互助互愛既行為，可以唔動容？<br />\n互不相識既香港人，為同一個理念走上街頭，追逐同一個理想既香港。仲可以唔支持示威人士？<br />\n<br />\n只有兩類人<br />\n一，既得利益者<br />\n二，唔了解示威行動，只睇tvb<br />\n<br />\n所以，面對第二類人，要虛心解釋佢知，咁無理既政府都忍左咁耐，依啲人點會忍唔到？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb5680fd102a163ef060c6f8bad2e511e179de2","tid":1439144,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021b3c21efabe15bb7f9ec46c3cd0ab6500959fc","tid":1439144,"uid":251292,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:38:55.000Z","msg":"點樣叫做唔講人話呢？<br />\n傳媒不嬲就係要中立，狙擊CCTVB係因為佢地偏頗。<br />\n耐唔耐就有啲打人罵有線同NOW變紅媒<br />\n大家有眼睇架<br />\n唔好覺得人地唔報示威者既好就罵<br />\n咁樣同藍絲冇分別"},{"pid":"8c92eeecdc28838ad88c7e73f14b7ca9947917f0","tid":1439144,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f0a914c8003be3628213870e0bfa37e2bbaa2d","tid":1439144,"uid":251292,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:39:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣叫做唔講人話呢？<br />\n傳媒不嬲就係要中立，狙擊CCTVB係因為佢地偏頗。<br />\n耐唔耐就有啲打<span style=\"color: red;\">手</span>罵有線同NOW變紅媒<br />\n大家有眼睇架<br />\n唔好覺得人地唔報示威者既好就罵<br />\n咁樣同藍絲冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d423101fa2efddc87ed0091d764a26e7a94a53f5","tid":1439144,"uid":282414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7937803663caf0746ac1813835060fe3811fae3e","tid":1439144,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:15:48.000Z","msg":"撐警既撐警<br />\n譴責暴力既譴責暴力<br />\n仲要繼續支持政府<br />\n而家警察<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無法無天，濫權濫捕</spa